                        <h2>Dear Participant,</h2>
                        <p style="font-size: 120%">Few days left till the #MBLT14 and we&nbsp;decided to&nbsp;gather the most important tips for our participants in&nbsp;this informational letter.</p>
                        <p>The first important thing we’d&nbsp;like to&nbsp;pay attention to&nbsp;is&nbsp;your profile on&nbsp;<nobr>runet-id</nobr>.com. We&nbsp;highly recommend to&nbsp;check your personal information including the name of&nbsp;the company you work for. This information will be&nbsp;shown on&nbsp;your badge.</p>
                        <p><img src="http://runet-id.com/img/mail/2014/20140521-mblt14-1.jpg?1" alt="" /></p>
                        <hr style="height: 1px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #F1F3F0; margin: 15px 0;" />
                        <h3>Official #MBLT14 app is&nbsp;already in&nbsp;AppStore!</h3>
                        <p>Now you can easily access the schedule, information about speakers, participants and find the map and address of&nbsp;the Digital October Center. Also you can find sections' description, list of&nbsp;speakers and participants in&nbsp;#MBLT14 app. Moreover if&nbsp;you are interested in&nbsp;speaker’s&nbsp;background, you can find their bio too.</p>
                        <p align="center" style="text-align: center"><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mblt-international-mobile/id638113300?mt=8#" style="display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; background: #28A9E0; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px; line-height: 14px; text-align: center; width: 230px;">DOWNLOAD APPLICATION</a></p>
                        <hr style="height: 1px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #F1F3F0; margin: 15px 0;" />
                        <p align="center"><img src="http://runet-id.com/img/mail/2014/20140521-mblt14-2.jpg?1" /></p>
                        <p>If&nbsp;you are thinking where to&nbsp;live in&nbsp;Moscow, we&nbsp;highly recommend the Mercure Moscow Paveletskaya Hotel. This new fashion hotel is&nbsp;the official partner of&nbsp;#MBLT14. You can book a&nbsp;room by&nbsp;phone +749572053 or&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mercure.com/gb/hotel-8223-mercure-moscow-paveletskaya/index.shtml">by&nbsp;web</a>.</p>
                        <hr style="height: 1px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #F1F3F0; margin: 15px 0;" />
                        <p><img src="http://runet-id.com/img/mail/2014/20140521-mblt14-4.jpg?1" alt="" /></p>
                        <p>Our official taxi partner Uber gives a&nbsp;discount for the first two rides. Just Install the app, tap in&nbsp;promo code MBLT14 and get to&nbsp;the conference by&nbsp;Mercedes S&nbsp;class. To&nbsp;calculate the ride you can <a href="https://www.uber.com/cities/moscow">here</a>.</p>
                        <hr style="height: 1px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #F1F3F0; margin: 15px 0;" />
                        <p><img src="http://runet-id.com/img/mail/2014/20140521-mblt14-3.jpg?1" align="right" style="float: right" />If&nbsp;you need assistance write at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:supportmoscow@uber.com">supportmoscow@uber.com</a>.</p>
                        <p>Official afterparty will be&nbsp;held in&nbsp;Simon Says Bar on&nbsp;Kudrinskaya square 1.</p>
                        <p>All the participant will be&nbsp;welcomed with drinks and snacks.</p>
                        <p>See you on&nbsp;May 23rd at&nbsp;#MBLT14!</p>
